ORBIT PULSE Theme for Wordpress

First of many goodies to be released, I've decided to Open Source the theme used for Orbit Pulse (http://www.orbitpulse.com).

It's being released under Creative Commons Share-alike licence. You must share a link to http://www.orbitpulse.com as an agreement to the licence. You may use the theme for personal and/or commercial purposes.

The complete licence can be found in the licence.html document.